                API documentation
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-semibold hover:text-blue-700 dark:hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors">
              Learn More
              <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Technical Consulting Service -->
        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-100 dark:from-purple-900/20 dark:to-pink-900/20 p-8 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Technology Consulting</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              Strategic technology guidance to help your organization make informed decisions about emerging technologies and digital transformation.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                AI strategy and implementation
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Technology architecture review
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Digital transformation planning
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Cloud migration strategies
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 font-semibold hover:text-purple-700 dark:hover:text-purple-300 transition-colors">
              Learn More
              <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Education & Training Service -->
        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-emerald-100 dark:from-green-900/20 dark:to-emerald-900/20 p-8 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-emerald-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Education & Training</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              Comprehensive training programs and educational resources to upskill your team in the latest technologies and development practices.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Custom training workshops
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Online course development
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Team skill assessments
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Certification programs
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 font-semibold hover:text-green-700 dark:hover:text-green-300 transition-colors">
